  <summary date="2018-05-15T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Educators Expense Deduction Modernization Act 

This bill amends the Internal Revenue Code, with respect to the deduction from gross income for certain expenses of elementary and secondary school teachers, to: (1) increase from $250 to $500 the annual limit on the expenses that may be deducted, and (2) require the limit to be adjusted for inflation after 2019.</summary>
